data.description: Centrally located spacious four bedroom three bath home in the highly desirable Bethany Trace community. Freshly painted exterior, all tile and laminate floors throughout, newer roof (2017), two spacious master suits, no homes to be built behind, very large large screened lanai, and central water and sewer. This home features four oversized bedrooms with the main master having a beautiful Trey ceiling and Master bath featuring dual sinks and separate tub and shower. The second master features a very spacious layout and a full bath with tub/shower combination. This bath can also be used as a pool bathroom if you decide to install a pool. The kitchen is very spacious and features plenty of cabinets, breakfast bar island, pantry and plenty of counter space. This home is an entertainers dream with a formal dining area, family room, and separate living room. The other nice features of this home are the spacious backyard and full laundry room.
